 Summary of the Pipeline we built:
 -------------------------
 Extract: Get raw text.
 Chunk: Recursive splitting (smart boundaries).
 Tokenize: Check token limits (Tiktoken).
 Tag: Add metadata (filename, date, user_id).
 Embed: Turn into vectors + Normalize.
 Store: Push to Pinecone/FAI

